data.description: A true family compound within a true family community! This multi-generational property on Autumn Maple comes with a guest house holding a separate mailing address, a gunite-finished pool surrounded by palm trees, and 6 total garages. From the gorgeous, real hardwoods, to the coffered ceilings, to the full bar and theater in the basement, this is an absolute must see and one-of-a-kind property. If you've ever played the Choteau golf course, you have driven under the bridge connecting the guest house and the main house! It is an extremely short drive once inside the community, which is a major asset, considering some homes take 10 minutes to get to after pulling through the gate. If you are unfamiliar about the Choteau Elan community, please ask me, because there is simply too much to type!
